PostgresqlFkPlugin
==================

Code was brought in from:
http://www.robbyonrails.com/articles/2005/11/11/rails-migrations-and-postgresql-constraints

I packaged it up into a plugin.

Example
=======

add_foreign_key(from_table, from_column, to_table)
drop_foreign_key(from_table, from_column, to_table)

